## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all possible strategies for strengthening achievement needs. Additionally, the information is limited to the context of McClelland's Theory of Needs and may not account for other motivational theories or individual differences within management teams. Further research and practical application are recommended to tailor strategies to specific organizational contexts.